query:
INSERT INTO task(
                        task_id,
                        queue_name,
                        status,
                        parent_task_id,
                        idempotency_key,
                        warehouse_id,
                        suspend_until)
        VALUES ($1, $2, 'pending', $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT unique_idempotency_key DO NOTHING
        RETURNING task_id
